WEBVTT

00:00.527 --> 00:01.476
There are two kinds of folks

00:01.533 --> 00:03.133
who sit around thinking
about how to kill people:

00:03.467 --> 00:05.193
Psychopaths
and mystery writers.

00:05.431 --> 00:06.453
I'm the kind that pays better.

00:06.854 --> 00:08.593
Who am I?
I'm Rick Castle.

00:08.683 --> 00:09.743
Castle.
Castle.

00:09.778 --> 00:11.478
I really am ruggedly handsome,
aren't I?

00:11.532 --> 00:13.722
Every writer needs inspiration.
And I found mine.

00:13.932 --> 00:14.751
Detective Kate Beckett.

00:14.998 --> 00:16.265
Beckett.
Aah!

00:16.538 --> 00:18.623
Beckett?
Could you get some backup, please?

00:18.974 --> 00:20.858
<i>And thanks to my friendship
with the Mayor,</i>

00:20.909 --> 00:22.543
<i>I get to be on her case.
Oh!</i>

00:22.577 --> 00:25.146
Do I look like a killer to you?
Yes, you kill my patience.

00:25.180 --> 00:26.814
<i>And together,
we catch killers.</i>

00:27.362 --> 00:30.264
I hate this case.
I know. Isn't it great?

