12:55.679 --> 12:57.727
Listen, Stu,
you want my guys oiled up

12:57.815 --> 13:00.067
in euro booty shorts for
the montage pool deck launch,

13:00.167 --> 13:02.602
you're gonna need to meet me
halfway here, buddy.

13:02.636 --> 13:05.588
Hey, be my guest. Shop around.
It's a fair rate.

13:05.622 --> 13:07.907
Listen, I gotta go.
I got guys here.

13:09.375 --> 13:11.810
My apologies. Promoters are
always a pain in my ass.

13:11.845 --> 13:14.247
- Lloyd Saunders--
- I'm already up to my ears in A-Rods.

13:14.914 --> 13:16.097
But, uh, your friend here--

13:16.257 --> 13:17.507
I got women requesting

13:17.532 --> 13:20.517
that skinny "Twilight" dude
like crazy.

13:21.915 --> 13:25.085
They're one size fits all.
We can pad if need be.

13:25.167 --> 13:27.602
Bathroom's down the hall
if you're shy.

13:27.623 --> 13:29.811
Hey, NYPD.

13:30.505 --> 13:32.772
We have some questions
about Derek Brookner.

13:32.807 --> 13:35.442
My mistake. We're doing
open auditions today.

13:35.476 --> 13:37.777
I can assure you,
this would fit.

13:37.811 --> 13:40.914
That's what they all say.
What about Derek?

13:40.948 --> 13:42.707
Well, he was murdered.

13:42.807 --> 13:44.775
Wow. Derek was
one of my best guys.

13:44.809 --> 13:47.778
We think he took a job that
might have got him into trouble.

13:47.812 --> 13:49.280
What kind of work did you book
